# OPTIONAL: server-side fallback Anthropic key.
# Not needed for public deployments — users bring their own key in the UI.
# Set this only if you want the app to work without users entering a key
# (e.g. internal/private deployments).
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Optional: model override. Defaults to claude-3-5-sonnet-latest.
# CLAUDE_MODEL=claude-3-5-sonnet-latest
